Benvolio!

198
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:43,040
Pan Romeo!

199
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:48,300
Romeo.

200
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,340
Dovol mi, abych tě ještě viděl.

201
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,000
Cielo se chtěl aspoň rozloučit.

202
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:59,720
